<D>__{sure.}
<C>__{lincoln}
<D>__{snagged my eye in the paper this morning. governor curtin is set to declare a winner in the disputed congressional election for the }
<C>__{w.n. bilbo}
<D>__{pennsylvania 16th district.}
<C>__{lincoln}
<D>__{what a joy to be comprehended. hop on a train to philadell, call on the governor }
<C>__{seward}
<P>__{(looking askance at bilbo's appearance:)}
<D>__{send latham. or schell.}
